Title: Systematic Resummed Perturbation Theory
Authors: Christof Wetterich
Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX
Report-no: HD-THEP-96-2
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A11 (1996) 2573-2584
\\
  A systematic loop expansion is formulated in terms of full propagators and
vertices. It is based on an expansion of the general solution of an exact
non-perturbative flow equation.
